location.fullValue: Tabor Plan, The Centre at Axiom

data.description: Come see this beautifully renovated end unit townhome with no HOA backing to greenspace. Located in the heart of Progress Ridge, this townhome is only 5 minutes walk from restaurants, shops, groceries and the lake. There is a 17 foot vaulted living room ceiling as you enter and see your remodeled kitchen with quartz countertops and stainless steel appliances. Luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout the main level except tiled bathrooms. 14 foot vaulted primary suite with adjoining bathroom and exceptional view. New seismically engineered deck with hot tub! Exterior was recently repainted. New furnace and AC! 2 car garage with new LED lighting. There is a walk in crawlspace that offers approximately 400 sq ft of additional storage space. Remodeled townhomes with no HOA, privacy, and walkability in such a desirable location don't come on the market very often! Get in before this one is gone! Open house from 1-3 PM Saturday Nov 18th.
